latestIgtvVideos.caption:
My pre-wedding shoot 💕 it’s already been 4 years to this, can’t believe 🥰
Took us three days to create this, we had chosen three different locations to shoot. 
Each shot came so naturally to us that we managed to wrap it up early. ☺️
It was September and we used to be sweating all the time, with all this makeup and multiple outfit changes.
Shooting the bonfire part was a task. Imagine sitting in front of a bonfire in september with leather jackets 😪

But it was all so worth it🤍
I remember @lakshyamanwani telling me that he had planned a shorter video but everything came out so well that video became this long. 

Captured beautifully by @safarnamafilms 
Location @theperfectlocationfaridabad @perfectpicturelocation 
MUA @shubhikapoor3
